{"tid":1191953,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先喺紅磡火車站等的士個三位絲打，對唔住","createTime":"2019-06-08T07:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T09:25:22.000Z","uid":45017,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e46ffff3fcad3668461ac7558eda41f2fd8497f8","tid":1191953,"uid":45017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:41:01.000Z","msg":"真係對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我見你地排得後左少少又睇緊電話，以為你地等緊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我好衰冇問過你地就爬左頭上左的士<br />\n我地互望個刻我覺得上又唔係落又唔係<br />\n卒之都係毒得滯淆左底上左車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係唔係有心打尖<br />\n在此再一次對你地講對唔住<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲打請瘋狂鬧我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab8c41d281fbb237dc7e7976803c4a7cdb9396d9","tid":1191953,"uid":40470,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:44:05.000Z","msg":"死毒撚個身勁臭"},{"pid":"3835f4b43742784915795cc3a362ba5422a3ba01","tid":1191953,"uid":128644,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:44:50.000Z","msg":"收爹啦屌你老母 搶左我地架的士"},{"pid":"671b7fe89aba525aa60f0865f8f590b4e583b21e","tid":1191953,"uid":61832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:44:50.000Z","msg":"惡過共產黨"},{"pid":"6c64f47309aad15a73b149de7fd196dfb83e882c","tid":1191953,"uid":71508,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:45:07.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦<br />\n見你咁靚仔<br />\n我地一齊玩4p la<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/